IN RE: Olander R. BYNUM No. 109P17-6 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 27, 2019 Olander R. Bynum, For Bynum, Olander R. Joseph Finarelli, Special Deputy Attorney General, For State of North Carolina

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Petitioner on the 21st of February 2019 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 27th of March 2019."
